<h2>You're Invited!</h2>

<p>Hi there!</p>

<p><strong class="highlight">{{inviterName}}</strong> has invited you to join their family <strong class="highlight">{{familyName}}</strong> on Luminous - the family command center.</p>

{{#if message}}
<div class="code-box">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-style: italic;">"{{message}}"</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>Use the invitation code below to join:</p>

<div class="code-box">
    <span class="code" style="letter-spacing: 4px;">{{invitationCode}}</span>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{acceptUrl}}" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
</p>

<p class="muted">This invitation expires on <strong>{{expiresAt}}</strong>.</p>

<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 30px 0;">

<h3>What is Luminous?</h3>

<p>Luminous is a digital family command center designed for busy households. With Luminous, you can:</p>

<ul>
    <li>View everyone's schedules at a glance</li>
    <li>Manage chores and routines</li>
    <li>Plan meals for the week</li>
    <li>Keep track of grocery lists and more</li>
</ul>

<p class="muted">
    If you don't know {{inviterName}} or didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
